overview:
* Partner: SEED Capital Management I/S
* Member of the Boards: UpCon Technology A/S, Mobintech A/S, IPBlaze A/S, Kaleido A/S, Nangate A/S and Stirling ApS

Career:

Peter has 20 years of operational experience in the ICT industry. Peter joined SEED Capital/DTU Innovation in 2003. Before this, he was a partner at Danske Venture Partners. Peter has been CTO in two 2MInvest backed startups, one of which was In2itive, which was sold to SPSS Inc. Previously, Peter worked for 4 years at Andersen Consulting (Accenture) as a Senior Consultant. Peter has a BSc in Electrical Engineering from the Danish Engineering Academy (1985).
